fatti. Dobbiamo andarcene.


485
00:51:05.616 --> 00:51:06.366
No.

486
00:51:06.367 --> 00:51:08.284
Tu devi andartene.

487
00:51:12.206 --> 00:51:13.206
Sì.

488
00:51:14.792 --> 00:51:16.960
