627
01:09:40.961 --> 01:09:45.790
<i>il loro dolore</i>

628
01:09:47.067 --> 01:09:52.224
<i>Presto vedremo</i>

629
01:09:53.211 --> 01:09:58.218
<i>quella bandiera sventolare</i>

630
01:10:00.041 --> 01:10:04.920
